    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108102\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">保羅</span>、<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108121\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">西拉</span>和<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108124\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">提摩太</span>曾在<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108128\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">帖撒羅尼迦</span>傳講<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108219\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">耶穌</span>。那是在<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108102\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">保羅的第二次旅程（保羅的旅程）</span>期間。這個故事記載在使徒行傳第17章。一些<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108503\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">猶太人</span>和許多<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108547\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">外邦人</span>相信了有關耶穌的信息。他們歡喜地接受了<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108043\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">好消息</span>。他們就像耶穌所說的落在好土裡的種子（太十三8、23）。有關耶穌的真理不僅僅是保羅大聲說出的話。真理伴隨著<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108388\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">聖靈</span>的能力而來。這種能力改變了帖撒羅尼迦<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108077\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">信徒</span>的生活。他們不再敬拜<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108284\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">假神</span>。他們在<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108232\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">信心</span>、愛心和盼望中變得堅強。他們成為其他信徒的榜樣。</p>",
