  {
    "content_id": 313344,
    "reference_id": 108996,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "帖撒羅尼迦前書 5:1–11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "52005001-52005011",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p>沒有人知道耶穌何時會再來到地上。保羅稱那個時候為<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108571\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">主的日子</span>。為了描述它，保羅用了耶穌關於產痛和夜間賊人的話（太24:8、43）。保羅談到耶穌的再來是<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108039\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">黑暗</span>和夜晚的結束。他也描述耶穌的再來是<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108546\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">光明</span>和白天的開始。保羅希望帖撒羅尼迦人以盼望來等候那個時刻。他們的盼望必須堅固，像頭盔一樣保護他們。他們的信心和愛是<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108157\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">屬靈的盔甲</span>。帖撒羅尼迦人要通過他們的盼望、信心和愛來互相鼓勵。</p>",
